{"tid":1547632,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"我宣佈搞黨鐵車站就係鬼","createTime":"2019-09-06T17:24:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T17:50:31.000Z","uid":306664,"like":1,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9b4222ca2fc61d03db6e5a4e1992a80b42e92202","tid":1547632,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:24:17.000Z","msg":"今日四條戇鳩仔喺油麻地站搞啲玻璃,搞啲燈 但係當大家喺度嗌<span style=\"color: red;\"> 五大訴求缺一不可  光復香港時代革命</span> 時 呢四條仆街完全唔出聲  我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你地係咪自己人呀？ 你哋居然一句都唔出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 佢哋今日嘅目的只有一個<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">破壞</span></strong> 當手足一齊嗌嗰時，完全冇理行埋一邊。 上個禮拜日又係咁 當手足要撤退嗰時就搞青衣站 搞到要大家幫手接放學 最後冇曬啲gear. 擺明就係幫狗剝去我哋嘅裝備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你係要搞都搞黨鐵嘅高層啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞個車站啲玻璃入閘機有撚用呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你只不過係搞到黨鐵連登嘅巴打絲打<br />\n搵唔到啲高層 畀錢買偵探查佢哋囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打爛幾塊玻璃有乜能用呀<br />\n<br />\n所以只有一個可能性 呢班仆街係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鬼</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港時代革命<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n因果由國容港治己<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"44669fa26b14f69a3cd506a1de73a3ad64f5ad75","tid":1547632,"uid":168449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:25:15.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"4c6e10ffd17258787d1e59f8646149455c223a20","tid":1547632,"uid":252292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:25:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/